data.text: What . A . Night! We are incredibly honored to be among the Kansas City Business Journal’s 2023 Champions of Business. Last night, we celebrated this achievement alongside 15 other incredible organizations. Thank you to the Kansas City Business Journal for shedding light on our people and projects and congratulations to all the recognized organizations! Hear from Dan Abitz on the organization’s approach to leadership, the secret to our success and the extensive growth we’ve experienced over the last few years. https://lnkd.in/g4AhSEuU Michelle Roberts Jim Jarrett Ben Lindner Hallie Sheptor Mackenzi Baum Shaun Kotwitz Doug Van Meter, PE
